Introduction It is an undeniable reality that by enlarging the female mind with education, there will be end to blind obedience, yet there are Various reasons which inhibit the process; consequently women across the globe suffer detrimental impacts. Hence, pragmatic policies and actions are needed to stream line women education ITUTE II. How strengthening the female mind by enlarging it with education Godsends blind obedience: 1.
